data.description: Picturesque 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom nestled in the heart of sought after High Point Terrace! Offering a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless elegance, this home features an inviting open-concept kitchen/living room perfect for family gatherings or cozy evenings! Split floor plan! Spacious bedrooms, gleaming hardwood floors, cedar beams, tons of natural light, brick patio, HUGE shed for storage, + more. Steps away from High point grocery, cheffies, greenline, etc.
